descriptionHtml: This mod hopefully fixes problems relating to the Dark Brotherhood quest: \"To Kill an Empire\" from starting even when console commands are used. It deletes previous Dark Brotherhood quest completion requirements and starts the quest game enabled. IMPORTANT: This mod will NOT work unless the console command \"setstage db09 00\" is used. The main thing this mod achieves is allowing the console commands to work as they should. Hope this solves the issue for you all, it did for me!
